<span id="Description"></span>
==Descrição== 

The [[Image:Draft_ShowSnapBar.svg|24px]] '''Draft ShowSnapBar''' command shows the Draft Snap toolbar. Some users only want to see this toolbar when a command is active and have changed their [[Draft_Snap#Preferences|preferences]] accordingly. For them this command is a way to show the toolbar to inspect, and optionally change, the [[Draft_Snap|snap options]].

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Utilização==

# Select the {{MenuCommand|Utilities → [[Image:Draft_ShowSnapBar.svg|16px]] Show Snap Toolbar}} option from the menu.

==Notes==

* Like any toolbar the Draft Snap toolbar can be toggled using these methods:
** Select the {{MenuCommand|View → Toolbars → Draft Snap}} option from the menu.
** Right-click an empty space in the [[Interface|toolbar area]] and select the {{MenuCommand|Draft Snap}} option from the menu that appears.


